name: BluntAbdominalTrauma
title: Blunt Abdominal Trauma
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains ICD-9 codes associated with Blunt Abdominal Trauma.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients with Blunt Abdominal Trauma.),(Inclusion Criteria: ICD-9 codes associated with Blunt Abdominal Trauma are included in this value set.),(Exclusion Criteria: Codes not associated with Blunt Abdominal Trauma are excluded from the value set.
